  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - XXVII. De se ipso.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Miraris, liquidum cur non dissolvor in amnem,</l>
     <l n="2">Quum numquam siccas cogar habere genas.</l>
     <l n="3">Miror ego, in tenues potius non isse favillas,</l>
     <l n="4">Assiduae carpant quum mea corda faces.</l>
     <l n="5">Scilicet ut misero possim superesse dolori;</l>
     <l n="6">Sic lacrimis flammas temperat acer Amor.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
